@@TJvImageListViewerOptions.FillCaption
Summary
  Specifies whether the background of captions are filled in their entirety or not.
Description
  Use FillCaption to specify whether the background of the caption of an item is filled in such a
  manner that the fill extends from the left to the right edge. If FillCaption is false, only the
  area covered by the caption is filled.
  
  FillCaption only affects selected items.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewerOptions.DrawingStyle
Summary
  Specifies the style to be used when an item is drawn.
Description
  Use the DrawingStyle property to control how an item is to appear. DrawingStyle controls how much
  of the blend color specified by the image list's BlendColor is combined with the foreground, or
  what background color to use.
See Also
  TJvImageListViewerOptions.SelectedStyle

