@@TJvImageListViewerOptions
Summary
  Options class for the TJvImageListViewer control.
Description
  TJvImageListViewerOptions is the class used for the Options property of a TJvImageListViewer. It
  derives from TJvCustomItemViewerOptions and publishes many of its properties as well as introducing
  new ones.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewer.Options
Summary
  Specifies the global options for the control.
Description
  Use Options to set the default behavior of the control.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewer.OnGetCaption
Summary
  Called when the control needs to get the caption to use for an item.
Description
  Write a handler for the OnGetCaption event when you want to provide captions for the items in a
  TJvImageListViewer.
Parameters
  Sender     - The object that triggered the event.
  ImageIndex - The index of the image in the image list to provide a caption for.
  ACaption   - The caption to draw along with the image.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewer.Images
Summary
  Lists images available for items in the TJvImageListViewer.
Description
  Images is a list of bitmaps that can be displayed for each item in the TJvImageListViewer. Each
  item in the control displays the image corresponding to the item's index in the control.

